153
01:39:18,000 --> 01:41:42,000
TRUE-ISH
In reality, the house wasn't in such a poor state. The door was still in place, albeit with broken hinges, & there were no goats. Not inside at least. There was one outside, chewing hay indifferently. 
154
01:41:42,000 --> 01:42:05,000
FALSE
He didn't step inside the house. He merely gazed in through the window. He didn't punch anything.
155
01:42:05,000 --> 01:42:19,000
TRUE-ISH
