156
01:42:19,000 --> 01:42:40,000
TRUE
Two men wandered over & one of them spoke good English. Saroo explained his story to him & showed him the sheet of scanned photos that he actually had with him. 
157
01:42:40,000 --> 01:43:54,000
TRUE-ISH
